    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some faded paint on the hood, and a few small door dings. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need a suspension tune-up and new tires in the near future. It is a solid foundation for anyone willing to put in a little work.",
