    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in showroom condition with no signs of wear. Every feature functions perfectly, and the car drives as smoothly as it did the day it left the lot. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in pristine, collectors-grade condition.",
