    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-cared-for ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure it's ready for many more miles. While it shows some light, honest wear from regular use, it remains a fantastic choice for anyone seeking a dependable and smooth-driving car!",
      "price": 34000.0,
